      "description": "The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes implementations) accurately predicts construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending loading conditions. Predicted QoIs fall within 10% of experimental mean values and the normalized error metric E/uval remains below 1.96 across all three quantities of interest, satisfying the pre-specified acceptance criteria for the COU.",
